Package com.raweng.built

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Built
    Contains all Built API classes and functions.
    BuiltACL
    A BuiltACL is used to control which users can access or modify a particular object.
    BuiltAnalytics
    The BuiltAnalytics class provides an interface to built.io's analytics backend.
    BuiltApplication
    To fetch application level information of your application from built.io server.
    BuiltDelta
    BuiltDelta fetch objects that are modified (created/updated/deleted) at/on specified date.
    BuiltError
    To retrieve information related to network call failure.
    BuiltEvent
    Helper class to set event uid and event properties required for analytics.
    BuiltExtension
    This class is used to make cloud related network calls.
    BuiltFile
    BuiltFile class to upload media files on built.io server.
    BuiltInstallation
    BuiltInstallation class for creating installation and subscribe/unsubscribe for push notifications against a channel.
    BuiltLocation
    This class is used to set location while creating new object or used for making geo point related queries.
    BuiltNotification
    To broadcast push notifications using built.io library.
    BuiltObject
    BuiltObject is used to create, update and delete built object on the built.io server.
    BuiltQuery
    A class that defines a query that is used to query for BuiltObject instance.
    BuiltRole
    To create, modify or delete roles on built.io server.
    BuiltUser
    This class allows registering user for an application and other features such as logging in and logging out.
    DeltaResult
    Helper class for parsing the result of BuiltDelta.
    FileObject
    Helper class to upload a single file with ACL and tags to built.io.
    QueryResult
    Helper class for parsing the result of BuiltQuery
    RoleObject
    To modify a role.
  • Enum Summary

    Built.LogType
    set an Info log message.
    BuiltError.ResponseType
    Response Type for error.
    BuiltQuery.CachePolicy
    cache policy.
    QueryResult.ResponseType
    Response Type of success query.
